entries.journal_entry_description: Nym has a slicer on retainer that can deactivate IG-88's security protocols. Find Kaibe and work with him to deactivate the security protocals.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Nym will be contacting you shortly.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: Hello there. I am glad that you have decided to take on my little problem. In order to get into the compound, you will need to fool the security system into believing you belong.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Nym says he has a slicer in his employ who may be able to crack the security codes on the factory entrance.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: You will find them at the Smugglers Outpost.
entries.task03_journal_entry_title: Meet with Kaibe's Associates on Endor
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Galody and Tupit have the data Kaibe needs to bypass the security profiles. Help them get the data to Kaibe.
entries.task04_journal_entry_title: Retrieve the data from Galody and Tupit
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Now that you have retrieved all the items, return to Kaibe. He will then assemble the remote slicing device.
entries.task05_journal_entry_title: Return to Kaibe with the items
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Travel to Endor and meet with Galody. He can help you gather the needed components.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Tupit can be found on Endor. She is an associate of Kaibe's. She can help you find some of the objects you need.
entries.task09_comm_message_text: Luckily I have someone on retainer who can do this. His name is Kaibe, and you can find him in my stronghold. Whatever question he has just answer by barking. Trust me on this.
